00:00:04.457 --> 00:00:08.992
based on some comments
that were made at TED two years ago

00:00:09.016 --> 00:00:12.665
about the need for the storage of vaccine.

00:00:12.689 --> 00:00:14.309
(Video): [On this planet

00:00:14.333 --> 00:00:16.848
1.6 billion people

00:00:16.872 --> 00:00:18.837
don't have access to electricity

00:00:18.861 --> 00:00:22.996
refrigeration

00:00:23.020 --> 00:00:25.637
or stored fuels

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.435
this is a problem

00:00:29.459 --> 00:00:31.775
it impacts:

00:00:32.265 --> 00:00:35.487
the spread of disease

00:00:35.511 --> 00:00:37.319
the storage of food and medicine

00:00:37.343 --> 00:00:40.445
